{
  "stem": "26609.17",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I knocked on the door, and said, go away, go away, go away, go away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't want to know you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I ran back to the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we matched a few kilometers to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You have seen it on the map.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was the first [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Americans were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we stayed there quite a while, until there was not-- it was, I think, in '46 that-- it was from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I think I have a photo of the Red Cross on my-- I have to find the photo I have there for the-- with the Red Cross here, Red Cross there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They looked for nurses to work there during our stay there in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But there are a lot of people, I think not hundreds but thousands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And later, they took me as a transport, because they were-- the doctors were still in the-- still in the fields.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We could hear shootings around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It wasn't straight away liberated all Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The Americans, and the Soviets, it was going on, and going on, all the times the war, different places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And-- but people wanted to go back-- not all, some wanted to stay there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And from there, to migrate wherever they could, United States or England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so we had no doctors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And through the Red Cross, it was established who wants to go back home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there were, I think, 8,000 that we had in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They all wanted to go back to Germany-- not Germany, Poland, Czechoslovakia, Romania, Hungary, mostly that part, eastern part of Europe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "In other places, there were others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I even didn't know that about three kilometers, I think, from the place where I stayed before, my sister was there as a non-Jewess, too.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
